Attempt to use hi-res images with Kindle, using Philip Greenspun's Travels With Samantha as an example.


To build:

Run 
$ ./build.sh

from the command line, and then
  open TravelsWithSamantha.mobi 
to launch the Kindle Mac app


The book was pulled from http://philip.greenspun.com/samantha/ using

  wget --mirror –w 2 –p -r –-convert-links –P . -I=samantha,images http://philip.greenspun.com/samantha/

(use brew install wget as necessary)
